vrlab.foodui.detectableObjects

Class FruitType

  • java.lang.Object
    • vrlab.foodui.detectableObjects.FruitType

  • public class FruitType
extends java.lang.Object
    class specifies a category of fruit, e.g. apple, banana, orange, and also the data belonging to this category - the class contains the name of the fruit type and also information, which is generated through a training
